Package gw.pl.external

Annotation Interface Invocation

@Deprecated @Target(METHOD) @Retention(RUNTIME) public @interface Invocation
Deprecated.
External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.
Describes how an external method is to be invoked internally.

    Modifier and Type
    Required Element

    name
    Deprecated.
